# Cursor rules (repo-local)
#
# This file is a compatibility shim for tools that still read legacy `.cursorrules`.
# Source of truth lives in:
# - `.agent/context.md`
# - `.agent/rules.md`
#
# Tool-specific rules are mirrored in:
# - `.cursor/rules/00-project-context.md` & `.cursor/rules/01-collaboration-rules.md` (Cursor)
# - `.claude/context.md` & `.claude/rules.md` (Claude Code)

## Project context (mirrored)
- Domain: MTG price tracker; Scryfall is source of truth for names / CN / oracle IDs.
- Matching: collector number + set + language + foil; normalize collector numbers (strip leading zeros).
- Shops: Hareruya active; track Buying (shop sell price) vs Selling (shop buyback/kaitori).

## Collaboration rules (mirrored)
- Make minimal, surgical edits; don’t add features not requested.
- Ask for clarification before destructive/large changes; don’t loop when stuck.
- Don’t add code comments unless requested.
- Run `npm run build` before suggesting deployment.
